  "text": "## FxVanillaOption Type Family Lineage in OpenGamma Strata\n\n### 1. Core Joda-Beans Domain Classes (modules/product/)\n\nThe four core domain classes form the foundation of the FX Vanilla Option type hierarchy:\n\n- **FxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java): The primary domain class representing a vanilla FX option contract. Annotated with @BeanDefinition, it implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxVanillaOption>. Properties include: longShort (LongShort), expiryDate (LocalDate), expiryTime (LocalTime), expiryZone (ZoneId), and underlying (FxSingle).\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java): Represents an OTC trade in FxVanillaOption with additional trade metadata. Implements FxOptionTrade and ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade>. Contains: info (TradeInfo), product (FxVanillaOption), and premium (AdjustablePayment).\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java): The resolved form of FxVanillaOption optimized for pricing. Implements ResolvedProduct. Contains: longShort (LongShort), expiry (ZonedDateTime), and underlying (ResolvedFxSingle). This is the input to pricer functions.\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java): The resolved trade form for pricing purposes. Implements ResolvedTrade. Contains: info (TradeInfo), product (ResolvedFxVanillaOption), and premium (Payment).\n\n### 2. Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\n\nThe project contains two pricing model variants with Product and Trade tier implementations:\n\n**Black Model Variant:**\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using the Black (lognormal) model. Uses DiscountingFxSingleProductPricer for underlying FX pricing and BlackFormulaRepository for option calculations.\n\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Extends Black pricing to the trade level, incorporating premium adjustments.\n\n**Vanna-Volga Model Variant:**\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Implements the Vanna-Volga pricing methodology, which adjusts Black prices for smile effects using three market instruments (ATM, Risk Reversal, Butterfly).\n\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Trade-level wrapper for Vanna-Volga pricing with premium handling.\n\n### 3. Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\n\nFour calculation classes wire the pricing layer to the calculation engine:\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java): Multi-scenario measure calculations aggregating Black and Vanna-Volga pricers. Contains methods for PV, Greeks, and other risk measures across scenario arrays.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMethod** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java): Enumeration defining the pricing methodology selection (Black vs Vanna-Volga).\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java): Integration point with the calculation engine, dispatching trades to appropriate measure calculations.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java): Single-scenario trade-level measure calculations.\n\n### 4. CSV Loader Plugin (modules/loader/)\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin** (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java): Implements TradeFile and CsvLoaderPlugin interfaces to parse FxVanillaOptionTrade instances from CSV files. Handles column mapping for trade metadata (ID, date), product fields (expiry, strike, currencies, notionals), and premium details.\n\n### 5. Dependency Reference: FxSingleBarrierOption\n\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java): A barrier option type that embeds FxVanillaOption as a core dependency. The class contains a property `underlyingOption` of type FxVanillaOption, creating a composition relationship where a single barrier option wraps a vanilla option with additional barrier and rebate specifications.\n\n### Type Resolution Chain\n\nThe type hierarchy follows a resolution pattern: `FxVanillaOption` → (via resolve()) → `ResolvedFxVanillaOption` and `FxVanillaOptionTrade` → (via resolve()) → `ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade`. This two-tier architecture separates contract specification from pricing-ready resolved forms, enabling efficient caching and batch processing of pricing requests.\n\n### Architectural Notes\n\n1. **Module Organization**: Clear separation of concerns across product (domain), pricer (computation), measure (integration), and loader (I/O) modules\n2. **Pricing Model Flexibility**: Support for both Black (simple) and Vanna-Volga (smile-aware) methodologies through parallel class hierarchies\n3. **Volatility Support**: Pricers leverage BlackFxOptionVolatilities and related surface classes for volatility term structures and smile dynamics\n4. **Integration Pattern**: The calculation function pattern delegates pricing decisions based on selected method (FxVanillaOptionMethod)"
}

